3D Walkthrough
Street View

With Jet liner views, location and resort style amenities this top floor Jr one Bedroom condo has it all. Luxury living at the highly coveted Hollywood Regis. The kitchen features stainless appliances, granite counter tops and ample room for cooking. The open concept floor plan allows you to enjoy the updated romantic fireplace and the city light views. The private balcony is perfect for morning coffee while enjoying city views. The spacious bedroom includes a massive walk-in closet with a in unit laundry. Enjoy the amenities of this resort style community including the heated pool, spa, fitness center, gated assigned parking, and on site management. Just blocks from Runyon Canyon Park, Runyon Canyon, many trendy restaurants, shopping, and nightlife . Complex is FHA approved!
